09:28.600 --> 09:29.350
Who's that?

09:30.910 --> 09:31.740
No one.

09:32.700 --> 09:34.360
Could you put it back?

09:34.560 --> 09:35.840
Doesn't look like a no one.

09:36.040 --> 09:37.840
Well, let me see.

09:38.040 --> 09:39.580
Aw, pretty.

09:39.780 --> 09:40.670
I said put it back.

09:40.870 --> 09:42.050
- Raw, raw, raw, eh?
- Feisty.

09:45.360 --> 09:47.410
You could do with
some loosening up.

09:50.410 --> 09:54.550
♪ No, I don't wanna be alone

09:54.750 --> 09:59.200
♪ I don't wanna be alone

10:02.290 --> 10:06.740
♪ Oh

10:06.940 --> 10:09.570
♪ I don't wanna be alone

10:09.770 --> 10:10.570
[plates clattering]

