he drank last night.

10:15.340 --> 10:16.390
Do you think he's okay?

10:17.790 --> 10:19.140
- [Kat] That's a nice
way of putting it.

10:19.340 --> 10:21.050
- [Naomi] Okay, he's
a hot fucking mess.

10:22.530 --> 10:24.670
Oh, don't even get me started.

10:24.870 --> 10:27.370
I mean, he's completely
lost without Tessa,

10:27.570 --> 10:29.150
but like, honey,
[Hardin's throat clears]

10:29.350 --> 10:30.450
you're never getting her back.

10:31.800 --> 10:33.680
[Hardin sighs]
[food sizzling]

10:33.880 --> 10:35.550
Look who's back from the dead.

10:35.750 --> 10:36.500
Fuck.

10:38.680 --> 10:40.240
I see you've raided my closet.

10:42.810 --> 10:45.170
[Kat chuckles]

10:45.370 --> 10:47.860
[horn honking]

10:49.560 --> 10:50.650
Ibuprofen?

10:50.850 --> 10:53.430
[pills rattling]

10:55.560 --> 10:57.910
- I've got a meeting so
you can let yourselves out.

11:00.050 --> 11:02.090
