17:17.410 --> 17:18.350
We have two options today.

17:18.550 --> 17:19.960
I'll just do another round.

17:20.160 --> 17:22.780
- [Flight Attendant]
Liquid lunch then.

17:22.980 --> 17:25.470
You can just keep 'em comin'.

17:27.170 --> 17:30.610
- [Flight Attendant] Who
