17:34.090 --> 17:36.360
Call it female intuition.

17:36.560 --> 17:37.790
Do you wanna talk about it?

17:40.140 --> 17:41.190
Not particularly, no.

17:42.530 --> 17:45.110
Well, if you change your mind,

17:45.310 --> 17:46.970
I will just be up there,

17:48.500 --> 17:49.930
